definition: to rise and fall/takeoff and landing/ups and downs

to rise/to raise/to get up/to set out/to start/to appear/to launch/to initiate (action)/to draft/to establish/to get (from a depot or counter)/verb suffix, to start/starting from (a time, place, price etc)/classifier for occurrences or unpredictable events: case, instance/classifier for groups: batch, group
to fall or drop/(of the sun) to set/(of a tide) to go out/to lower/to decline or sink/to lag or fall behind/to fall onto/to rest with/to get or receive/to write down/whereabouts/settlement
colloquial reading for 落[luo4] in certain compounds
to leave out/to be missing/to leave behind or forget to bring/to lag or fall behind
vertical or short takeoff and landing aircraft

sentences.english: Our last five years were marked by uncertainty and rapid change.
sentences.chinese: 过去五年，我们的大环境起落不定，变化快速。

sentences.english: It also states a troubleshooting analysis of the undercarriages retractile system.
sentences.chinese: 还包括一次起落架收放系统的故障分析。

sentences.english: We've got to overshoot, we're having difficulties with the landing gear.
sentences.chinese: 我们复飞，我们起落架处境困难。

sentences.english: Embrace your life with all the ups and down.
sentences.chinese: 拥抱你生活中所有的起起落落。

sentences.english: Please wipe excess oil from engine nacelles and landing gears.
sentences.chinese: 擦掉发动机吊舱和起落架上多余的油。
几乎更换了左侧主起落架内侧轮胎。

sentences.english: Test of Semiactive Landing Gear Control For a General Aviation Aircraft.
sentences.chinese: 一种通用航空飞机半主动起落架控制的试验。

sentences.english: The aircraft's undercarriage retracted as it climbed into the air.
sentences.chinese: 飞机的起落架在升空时即可缩回。

sentences.english: A dynamic model of landing gear struts is introduced in a non-inertial coordinate system.
sentences.chinese: 在非惯性坐标系中建立了起落架支柱的动力学模型。

sentences.english: Notice that the movement of your belly and chest rises and falls like the motion of rolling waves.
sentences.chinese: 注意，腹部和胸部的起落运动，就像翻滚的波浪。

sentences.english: The past years had known him in many weathers.
sentences.chinese: 过去的岁月里，他起起落落。

sentences.english: Other-worldly chanting, to the rhythm of the rising and falling picks resonated through the hot, still air.
sentences.chinese: 闷热的空气里回荡着圣歌的旋律和镐斧起落的声音。

sentences.english: Check the L MLG hydraulic tube leakage is out of limits.
sentences.chinese: 检查发现左主起落架一液压管漏油超标。

sentences.english: Yet the past year, the Year of the Ox, turned out to be full of fluctuations and changes.
sentences.chinese: 刚过去的牛年，充满起落和变化。

sentences.english: Some important issues such as the increase of the load of the nose landing-gear are analyzed.
sentences.chinese: 文章中还分析了分级甲板会增大前起落架载荷等问题。
